	* configure.in: Added "hi" to ALL_LINGUAS.

2003-09-04 Damien Sandras  <dsandras@seconix.com>

	* src/endpoint.cpp: Added 127.0.0.1 to the list of IP's that
	shouldn't be translated. (thanks to Roger Hardiman)
	
